message.body: The last two Wednesdays did not cooperate, but I should be able to walk with you and ###### tomorrow if you don't mind :)
I don't mind at all, but I'm have a "questioning-my-purpose-in-life" kind of bad week, and it is only Tuesday, so u walk at ur own risk :)
Oh no! Well then I can at least offer an ear to listen :)
Just let me know what time you think you'll be heading out
Will do. Let me see how my day is going tomorrow and I'll get back to you.

I hate to do this but can I get a raincheck on the walk? ##### needs my help to bring stuff to his new home (officially as of today) in ## and I'm heading to ## tomorrow and still need to pack. I promise we can start Wed walks beginning next week!
Yay! Sorry for the late notice. Hopefully next Wednesday's walk will also be less wickedly windy!
